HTTP Status Error Code Cause Resolution <code>401</code> <code>UNAUTHORIZED</code> Key is missing or malformed Add a valid <code>X-API-Key</code> header <code>401</code> <code>UNAUTHORIZED</code> Key has been revoked Request a new key from support <code>429</code> <code>RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED</code> Too many requests Wait and retry after the reset window <p>Example 401 response:</p> <pre><code>{
  "errorCode": "UNAUTHORIZED",
  "message": "Invalid or missing API key"
}
</code></pre>
